rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0001
rows.name: Maybe in bit of small big trouble...

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Cargo ship that was on way to
Goldmund has run aground...

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Trade people already come to pick up
ship itself...

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0004
rows.name:
But ship very smashed up all over.
Not able to sail any more.

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Maintenance team already busy
working on different ship, so have
big lack of manpower for repairs.

rows.label: tlk42450111_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, if friends could!
Would be massive help to Koikoi!
